o common shares, the bank also offers two issuances of preferred stock, a floating rate Series D (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1323945865/image_1323945865.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741625-synovus-financial-series-e-dividends-provide-best-yield-despite-premium-price", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 06:59:12"}, {"id": "4741624", "title": "Despite G700 Delivery Delays, General Dynamics Appears On Track", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/544451913/image_544451913.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aircraft engineers inspecting jet engine in aircraft maintenance factory\" data-id=\"544451913\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/544451913/image_544451913.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/544451913/image_544451913.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/544451913/image_544451913.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/544451913/image_544451913.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/544451913/image_544451913.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/544451913/image_544451913.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/544451913/image_544451913.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/544451913/image_544451913.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Monty Rakusen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In January 2024, I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4665690-general-dynamics-q4-g700-certification-is-delayed-but-on-the-way-initiate-with-strong-buy\">initiated</a> a \u2018Strong Buy\u2019 rating on General Dynamics (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GD\" title=\"General Dynamics Corporation\">GD</a></span>) highlighting its strong backlog growth amid global geopolitical tensions. They delivered 10.4% revenue growth and 11.7% operating profit growth in <a href=\"https://s22.q4cdn.com/891946778/files/doc_financials/2024/q3/GD-2024-09-29-Exhibit-99-1.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">Q3</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/544451913/image_544451913.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741624-despite-g700-delivery-delay-general-dynamics-stock-on-track", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 06:54:41"}, {"id": "4741623", "title": "Solid Power: Testing Investors' Patience", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119005314/image_119005314.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bored senior man passing time in a waiting room\" data-id=\"119005314\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119005314/image_119005314.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119005314/image_119005314.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119005314/image_119005314.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119005314/image_119005314.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119005314/image_119005314.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119005314/image_119005314.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119005314/image_119005314.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119005314/image_119005314.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andrew Bret Wallis/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><span>Performance Assessment</span></h2> <p>My last 'Sell' view on Solid Power (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SLDP\" title=\"Solid Power, Inc.\">SLDP</a></span>) has played out well as the stock has underperformed the S&amp;P500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPY\" title=\"SPDR\u00ae S&amp;P 500 ETF Trust\">SPY</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPX\" title=\"S&amp;P 500 Index\">SPX</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IVV\" title=\"iShares Core S&amp;P 500 ETF\">IVV</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VOO\" title=\"Vanguard S&amp;P 500 ETF\">VOO</a>):</p> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>I am retaining my bearish view after <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/filing/9224510\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/filing/9224510\" target=\"_blank\">Q3 FY24 results</a>:</p> <ol> <li>A-2 cell delivery timelines</li> </ol>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119005314/image_119005314.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741623-solid-power-earnings-underperformance-downtrend-still-intact", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 06:40:28"}, {"id": "4741622", "title": "Bausch Health Companies: Improving Core Business Cures Its Bankruptcy Rumors", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420833002/image_1420833002.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bausch Health US headquarters in Bridgewater, NJ, USA.\" data-id=\"1420833002\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420833002/image_1420833002.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420833002/image_1420833002.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420833002/image_1420833002.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420833002/image_1420833002.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420833002/image_1420833002.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420833002/image_1420833002.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420833002/image_1420833002.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420833002/image_1420833002.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Bausch Health Companies</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BHC\" title=\"Bausch Health Companies Inc.\">BHC</a></span>, <span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">TSX:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BHC:CA\" title=\"Bausch Health Companies Inc.\">BHC:CA</a></span>) is one of the undervalued stocks currently, trading only at trailing EV/EBITDA of 8.03x. The expected complete spin-off of its Bausch + Lomb (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BLCO\" title=\"Bausch + Lomb Corporation\">BLCO</a>) will have more benefit</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420833002/image_1420833002.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741622-bausch-health-companies-improving-core-business-cures-its-bankruptcy-rumors", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 06:21:03"}, {"id": "4741621", "title": "Realty Income Vs. Agree Realty: Is The Valuation Gap Justified", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1195575719/image_1195575719.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Chess concept\" data-id=\"1195575719\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1195575719/image_1195575719.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1195575719/image_1195575719.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1195575719/image_1195575719.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1195575719/image_1195575719.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1195575719/image_1195575719.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1195575719/image_1195575719.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1195575719/image_1195575719.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1195575719/image_1195575719.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Kubra Cavus</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Investors often compare Agree Realty (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ADC\" title=\"Agree Realty Corporation\">ADC</a></span>) and Realty Income (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/O\" title=\"Realty Income Corporation\">O</a></span>), as these are both triple-net lease REITs concentrating (predominantly in the case of O and completely in the case of ADC) on retail-oriented properties and both</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1195575719/image_1195575719.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741621-realty-income-vs-agree-realty-is-the-valuation-gap-justified", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 06:06:42"}, {"id": "4741617", "title": "RING ETF And China's Massive Gold Mining Discovery", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173870408/image_173870408.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Macro picture of a raw golden nugget found on a mine\" data-id=\"173870408\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"2800px\" height=\"1874px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173870408/image_173870408.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173870408/image_173870408.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173870408/image_173870408.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173870408/image_173870408.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173870408/image_173870408.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173870408/image_173870408.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173870408/image_173870408.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173870408/image_173870408.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">plastic_buddha</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>If you have already heard about the recent discovery of the world's largest deposit of gold in China, you are probably wandering the web to understand what the impact on gold prices could be.</p> <p>Effectively, in my humble opinion, this discovery could</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173870408/image_173870408.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741617-ring-etf-china-massive-gold-mining-discovery", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 04:56:30"}, {"id": "4741613", "title": "Tracking Dan Loeb's Third Point Portfolio - Q3 2024 Update", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Magnifying glass on top of financial market info\" data-id=\"186805810\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3872px\" height=\"2592px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">SusanneB</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article is part of a series that provides an ongoing analysis of the changes made to Dan Loeb\u2019s 13F stock portfolio on a quarterly basis. It is based on Third Point\u2019s regulatory <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1040273/000108514624005927/0001085146-24-005927-index.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">13F Form</a> filed on 11/14/2024. Please</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741613-tracking-dan-loebs-third-point-portfolio-q3-2024-update", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 04:30:27"}, {"id": "4741612", "title": "Muni Bond Funds Are Attractive Now If You Have Large Taxable Assets", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1350489578/image_1350489578.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Municipal bonds is shown on the business photo using the text\" data-id=\"1350489578\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1350489578/image_1350489578.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1350489578/image_1350489578.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, 